<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<h1>Observability Demo</h1>

<p>This demo showcases .NET Aspire's built-in observability features:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Distributed Tracing</strong> — See request flows across services</li>
    <li><strong>Metrics</strong> — Custom counters and histograms</li>
    <li><strong>Structured Logging</strong> — Rich log data with named parameters</li>
</ul>

<p>Try these API endpoints to generate telemetry:</p>
<ul>
    <li><code>/weatherforecast</code> — Normal request with structured logs</li>
    <li><code>/slow</code> — Slow request with custom spans (check Traces in the dashboard)</li>
    <li><code>/error</code> — Error request (check Structured Logs for the exception)</li>
</ul>
